# Deck layout sandbox — local only, must never ship. It sits outside /deck, so it has no auth
# guard, and it reads real client decks (with budgets) straight from Supabase. Kept on disk
# because tuning a layout change across all 18 slides at once is what it is for; ignored here so
# a `git add -A` can't put it back into a public repo. Was removed once already in 83b4f51.
# Brackets escaped: unescaped, gitignore reads [locale] as a character class and never matches
# the literal Next.js dynamic-segment folder.
app/\[locale\]/lab/
